; *                                                                            *
; *                      VERBS AFFECTING LIT/UNLIT STATUS                      *
; *                                                                            *
; ******************************************************************************
; Ensure that only the correct verbs can be used with natural and artificial
; light sources.
; ==============================================================================
; NATURAL LIGHT SOURCE: CANDLE
; ==============================================================================
; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; ALLOWED VERBS
; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; The following verbs can be used with natural light sources:
; VERB `extinguish`
extinguish candle
put out candle
put candle out
; VERB `light`
light candle
; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; ILLEGAL VERBS
; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; The following verbs can not be used with natural light sources:
; VERB `turn_on`
turn on candle
switch on candle
; VERB `turn_off`
switch off candle
turn off candle
; ==============================================================================
; ARTIFICIAL LIGHT SOURCE: FLASHLIGHT
; ==============================================================================
; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; ALLOWED VERBS
; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; The following verbs can be used with artificial light sources:
; VERB `light`
light flashlight
; VERB `switch`
switch flashlight
switch flashlight
; VERB `turn_on`
turn on flashlight
turn flashlight on
switch on flashlight
switch flashlight on
; VERB `turn_off`
turn off flashlight
turn flashlight off
switch off flashlight
switch flashlight off
; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; ILLEGAL VERBS
; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; The following verbs can not be used with natural light sources:
; VERB `extinguish`
; ***BUG!*** The verb is not being blocked! (See #123)
extinguish flashlight
put out flashlight
put flashlight out
